        <updateDate>2022-05-25T12:41:13Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fission for the Future Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill supports the commercial deployment of advanced nuclear reactors. Specifically, the Department of Energy (DOE) must establish a program that provides financial assistance for the commercial planning, licensing, development, and construction of (1) advanced nuclear reactors, or (2) supply chain infrastructure associated with such reactors or related technologies.</p> <p>In addition, the bill reauthorizes through FY2027 and revises a DOE program designed to strengthen university research and training in nuclear science and engineering.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
